
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
	<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/b99e675b6e.js"></script>

	<title>Luca Imbrogno - Stock Trading Game</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1 id="main-title">LUCA IMBROGNO</h1>

<%= render :partial => "/utilities/mobile_nav" %>

<div class="wrapper">

    <div class="sidebar">
			<%= render :partial => "/utilities/header" %>
    </div>

    <div class="main_content">
		<div class="header">Trading Simulation</div>
        <a href="/projects" class="back">
            <i class="fas fa-angle-left"></i>  Back To Projects
        </a>
		<div class="info stock-game-info">
			<div>Simply enter the stock ticker you want to trade or use the default AAPL data and press start to begin the simulation. Use the BUY and SELL buttons to trade one share at a time as the simulation runs. This graph is roughly the last 5 months of daily historical stock data from AlphaVantage. After the simulation is complete, check your total realized profit below. Coming soon: compete against my own trading algorithm to see if you can beat the computer!</div>
		</div>
      	<%= render :partial => "/trading_strategies/stock_chart" %>

        <div class="stock-game-container">
            <div  id="stock-selections">
                Enter Ticker:<br>
                <input type="text" class="stock-ticker">
                <br><br>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="findStock()">Find Stock</button>
            </div>

            <div class="info" id="controls">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" id="start-button" name="button" onclick="runSim()">
                    Start
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" id="reset-button" name="button" onclick="reset()">
                    Reset
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" id="buy-button" name="button" onClick="buy()">
                     BUY
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" id="sell-button" name="button" onClick="sell()">
                    SELL
                </button>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="text-results">
                    Your Realized Profit <br>
                </div>
                <div class="value-results">

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
		<div class="notes">
			<p><strong>Project Notes:<br></strong> Tools used to build this project: AlphaVantage Stock API, Highcharts Library </p>
		</div>
	</div>

</div>



	<script type="text/javascript" src="http://code.highcharts.com/stock/highstock.js"></script>
	<%= javascript_include_tag "mobile_nav_animations"  %>
	<%= javascript_include_tag "trading"  %>
</body>
</html>
